      "message": "[Critical] Line 52: `setLimits()` accepts invalid limits such as `minKbps \u003e maxKbps`, but `std::clamp` has undefined behavior when the low bound is greater than the high bound. Validate or normalize the inputs before storing them.\\n```suggestion\\n    if (minKbps \u003e maxKbps)\\n        std::swap(minKbps, maxKbps);\\n    cfg_.minBitrateKbps \u003d minKbps;\\n    cfg_.maxBitrateKbps \u003d maxKbps;\\n```",
